list.item: RECORD GROUP 1: AMERICAN FEDERATION OF TEACHERS, LOCAL 1485/YAKIMA VALLEY COLLEGE FEDERATION OF TEACHERS
SERIES I: COLLECTIVE BARGAINING AND CONTRACTS
RECORD GROUP 2: EDMONDS-EVERETT ASSOCIATION FOR HIGHER EDUCATION

scopecontent.p: Correspondence, collective bargaining and proposals, Executive Board minutes 1988-1996, arbitration files, and related files of the local. Includes documentation on reductions in the community college's instructional staff due to budget constraints, as well as files related to bargaining procedures.
